
gui - implement the GUI!

collections-manager - create a system for managing all Collections

auto-sync - use event system to allow syncing of track info changes among the various parts automatically (depends: collections-manager)

library-watching - allow watching a Library for updates (periodic or real-time)

xspf-playlists - support xspf playlists fully

playlist-manager - create a system for managing all Playlists

custom-stemming - allow trimming of 'A', not just 'The'

keyboard-shortcuts - allow more control via keyoard, eg. pressing 'Enter' in collection pane should add selection to current playlist (depends: gui)

xdg-dirs - store our data and config according to XDG spec - http://standards.freedesktop.org/basedir-spec/basedir-spec-0.6.html
